{"tid":1464271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[少少建議]其實需唔需要整幾條戒律，用黎團結各人?","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:27:24.000Z","uid":67454,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"85579cd3d8fb20102b1b92962f0f3cb5ef39c856","tid":1464271,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:43:26.000Z","msg":"睇返中共紅軍成立初期，老毛為左令班人有紀律而list左幾條rule出黎，從而令成支紅軍慢慢變成有組織性既部隊<br />\n<br />\n紅軍三大紀律：<br />\n一切行動聽指揮；<br />\n不拿群眾一針一線；<br />\n一切繳獲要歸公。<br />\n<br />\n八項注意：<br />\n說話和氣；<br />\n買賣公平；<br />\n借東西要還；<br />\n損壞東西要賠償;<br />\n不打人罵人；<br />\n不損壞莊稼；<br />\n不調戲婦女；<br />\n不虐待俘虜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知今次大家都反對大台主意，所以有D唔可以照搬，而且係靠自律，但為左確保唔會再互相猜疑玩捉鬼，我覺得有需要整一D general rule出黎比大家遵守，但只要唔違反就可以隨意做，大家各自爬山"},{"pid":"d0aafb0b02dfca4882ab1ef401ef85722732d200","tid":1464271,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:45:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3e00b462c7db93f0427f93d9886e772be7132c1","tid":1464271,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:47:21.000Z","msg":"例如今日咁，大家諗定捉到懷疑黑警/公安，可以跟咩程序去做，咁就唔洗懷疑周圍有鬼煽動"},{"pid":"20f2899e3ee01ea2a2ee2721c6e3e94b6dd381e9","tid":1464271,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:02:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea29fc11d9f7bd8f0d40de95eb75b283e804a52e","tid":1464271,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4bba5486a9c7a41f20d3788f68854193d4e1943","tid":1464271,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6581e975ef48e7965542f5736e82e7d0a0d3a7ca","tid":1464271,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:53:11.000Z","msg":"認同 但一切要前線又好冷氣又好黑衫白衫都認同嘅準則<br />\n<br />\n確保越規者 一率是為敵人 <br />\n<br />\n另外 捉鬼後應對方針 都要定 早起女犬扮商人時已經要制定<br />\n<br />\n但 非急切性可聽日先"},{"pid":"877b1126e2069e86e96ee38d288833ba02735aa7","tid":1464271,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6581e975ef48e7965542f5736e82e7d0a0d3a7ca","tid":1464271,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:53:11.000Z","msg":"認同 但一切要前線又好冷氣又好黑衫白衫都認同嘅準則<br />\n<br />\n確保越規者 一率是為敵人 <br />\n<br />\n另外 捉鬼後應對方針 都要定 早起女犬扮商人時已經要制定<br />\n<br />\n但 非急切性可聽日先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:59:02.000Z","msg":"多謝意見"},{"pid":"22844621428f5fb03eeed793eae36efcd2f5a7df","tid":1464271,"uid":303862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:07:00.000Z","msg":"憲兵隊"},{"pid":"3ad003df54ada71a29c892393b7451618c9bdace","tid":1464271,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:27:24.000Z","msg":"push"}]}